author: uing
title: Eric Nam Unveils Flowery Teaser For Upcoming Collaboration Track
text:
Eric Nam is releasing a new track titled “You, Who?” on March 9! 
On March 6, he uploaded a teaser image on his official social media, announcing a comeback. According to the image, the track will be a collaboration with someone yet to be revealed. 
This release is special, as it marks the beginning of Eric Nam’s new collaboration project called “Spring Note,” for which he plans to release new music every spring. The name “Spring Note” is a double entendre that signifies both “a notebook for memories” and “a musical note in spring,” 
His collaboration partner will be revealed on March 7, while the song “You, Who?” is set for release on March 9 at 6 p.m. KST. 
Can you guess who his collaboration partner might be?
